    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到TAU星系，空间站指挥官！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242950/extras/e1572d70f23b88714b41986b143038de.avif?t=1759326923\" width=1054 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>建造</strong>、<strong>扩张并利用</strong>一切可用资源，打造横跨行星的太空工业集群，其规模之宏大将为星系前所未见。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在追求极致工业掌控的征程中，您将建造<strong>机器人货船</strong>、<strong>人工虫洞</strong>，甚至驾驭<strong>反物质</strong>的强大力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242950/extras/4e69c76a9e9d8c89b2d4e70c52173131.avif?t=1759326923\" width=1054 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将<strong>小行星原子化、开采矿石</strong>、部署<strong>云矿机</strong>，通过多种方式采集原材料，并将其加工为高级材料、成品物品与精密零件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 建立<strong>精密供应链</strong>，<strong>实现资源采集自动化</strong>，<strong>优化</strong>空间站配置，以最高效率达成您的目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242950/extras/7715d62124a80f57f6c76f4fb33edea8.avif?t=1759326923\" width=1054 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>建造星舰</strong>以完成目标，并解锁日益先进的科技，助您完成掌控这片敌对外星恒星系的使命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>民用</strong>与<strong>军用</strong>舰船需要迥异且更复杂的建造技术——其中某些技术对您和空间站的风险远高于其他。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242950/extras/d2b47fd9480ac99f37f90dae8545c862.avif?t=1759326923\" width=1054 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>多个行星</strong>上<strong>建立多座空间站</strong>，以开采稀有资源，并通过虫洞将其连接，构建星际供应链。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>但需警惕</strong>：您并非这片外星恒星系中的唯一势力，必须做好自身与空间站的<strong>防护</strong>方能在此立足发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242950/extras/16a5b7248e9b8723f7ee38cb51dd335f.avif?t=1759326923\" width=1054 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沿途回收<strong>神秘的外星遗物</strong>，利用它们为您的空间站和无人机解锁强力升级——助您扫清前行之路的一切阻碍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>升级</strong>武器、加装护盾或加力推进器以自如穿梭危险星域，或提升空间站能源与生产效率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242950/extras/ef7f8e050a1324383ac026288fc22ffe.avif?t=1759326923\" width=1054 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>在线PVE合作模式</strong>中与最多4名玩家<strong>组队</strong>，共同分担探索、战斗与建造任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在团队间共享<strong>任务与待办清单</strong>，实现效率最大化。</p>",
